{
  "id": "south-measure-hall-ressa-venn",
  "title": "Susanna Fontana at the Council Table",
  "nodes": {
    "start": {
      "lines": [
        "Susanna leaves the water roll open at the center of the table. Every available chair faces it."
      ],
      "choices": [
        {
          "label": "Review what remains undecided",
          "next": "review"
        },
        {
          "label": "Choose emergency feed closure",
          "conditions": {
            "flags": [
              "south-measure-water-decision-open",
              "intake-clerk-resolved"
            ],
            "flagsAbsent": [
              "south-measure-plan-monitored-flow",
              "south-measure-plan-morrow-import",
              "south-measure-plan-isolated-loop",
              "south-measure-plan-feed-closed"
            ]
          },
          "effects": {
            "setFlag": [
              "south-measure-plan-feed-closed",
              "feed-closure-selected"
            ],
            "log": "South Measure will close the buried feed and survive on emergency water."
          },
          "next": "plan-closed",
          "tone": "commit"
        },
        {
          "label": "Commit the chosen water plan",
          "conditions": {
            "questStages": {
              "names-for-the-gate": "choose-water-plan"
            },
            "flagsAtLeast": {
              "count": 1,
              "of": [
                "south-measure-plan-monitored-flow",
                "south-measure-plan-morrow-import",
                "south-measure-plan-isolated-loop",
                "south-measure-plan-feed-closed"
              ]
            }
          },
          "next": "operate"
        },
        {
          "label": "Continue the settlement decisions",
          "next": "decisions"
        },
        {
          "label": "Leave the council table",
          "close": true,
          "tone": "quiet"
        }
      ]
    },
    "review": {
      "lines": [
        "\"Resolve the Clerk before choosing water. Once water has a plan, settle who holds the keys and roll; Noa and Cassian must answer for their own departures.\"",
        "\"The road opens after those names are spoken in public. I will not trade the order for speed.\""
      ],
      "choices": [
        {
          "label": "Withdraw the Compact monitoring plan",
          "conditions": {
            "flag": "south-measure-plan-monitored-flow"
          },
          "effects": {
            "clearFlag": [
              "south-measure-plan-monitored-flow",
              "compact-monitoring-agreement",
              "compact-monitoring-supervised",
              "compact-monitoring-compelled"
            ],
            "setFlag": "compact-monitoring-withdrawn",
            "log": "Aurelia withdraws the monitoring rota. The water plan remains open."
          },
          "next": "start",
          "tone": "commit"
        },
        {
          "label": "Cancel the Morrow cistern plan",
          "conditions": {
            "flag": "south-measure-plan-morrow-import"
          },
          "effects": {
            "clearFlag": [
              "south-measure-plan-morrow-import",
              "morrow-water-contract",
              "morrow-water-exchange",
              "morrow-water-purchased",
              "morrow-water-compelled"
            ],
            "setFlag": "morrow-water-plan-cancelled",
            "log": "Darius strikes the cistern schedule. The water plan remains open."
          },
          "next": "start",
          "tone": "commit"
        },
        {
          "label": "Set aside the isolated-loop plan",
          "conditions": {
            "flag": "south-measure-plan-isolated-loop"
          },
          "effects": {
            "clearFlag": [
              "south-measure-plan-isolated-loop",
              "resident-isolation-selected"
            ],
            "setFlag": "resident-isolation-deferred",
            "log": "Noa leaves the isolation marks in place. The water plan remains open."
          },
          "next": "start",
          "tone": "commit"
        },
        {
          "label": "Return to the decision",
          "next": "start"
        },
        {
          "label": "Leave",
          "close": true,
          "tone": "quiet"
        }
      ]
    },
    "decisions": {
      "lines": [
        "Susanna turns the decision slate to the first unfinished line."
      ],
      "choices": [
        {
          "label": "Decide control of the pump",
          "conditions": {
            "questStages": {
              "names-for-the-gate": "decide-pump-control"
            }
          },
          "next": "pump"
        },
        {
          "label": "Decide custody of the original roll",
          "conditions": {
            "questStages": {
              "names-for-the-gate": "decide-roll-custody"
            }
          },
          "next": "roll-consent"
        },
        {
          "label": "Settle Noa Faber’s departure",
          "conditions": {
            "questStages": {
              "names-for-the-gate": "settle-nel"
            }
          },
          "next": "nel"
        },
        {
          "label": "Settle Brother Cassian’s departure",
          "conditions": {
            "questStages": {
              "names-for-the-gate": "settle-tarn"
            }
          },
          "next": "tarn"
        },
        {
          "label": "Call the north-gate assembly",
          "conditions": {
            "questStages": {
              "names-for-the-gate": "north-gate-assembly"
            }
          },
          "next": "assembly"
        }
      ]
    },
    "plan-closed": {
      "lines": [
        "Susanna writes FEED CLOSED across the water board.",
        "\"The pipe goes quiet. The arrival fires drink from storage until storage is gone.\""
      ],
      "choices": [
        {
          "label": "Commit the operating plan",
          "next": "operate"
        }
      ]
    },
    "operate": {
      "lines": [
        "Noa waits at the feed board. The hall listens for an answer through the floor pipes."
      ],
      "choices": [
        {
          "label": "Open monitored full flow",
          "conditions": {
            "flag": "south-measure-plan-monitored-flow"
          },
          "effects": {
            "setFlag": "south-measure-water-full",
            "questUpdate": {
              "quest": "names-for-the-gate",
              "stage": "decide-pump-control",
              "log": "Compact monitors hold the buried rhythm below the tap cycle. Every row receives water."
            },
            "clearFlag": [
              "south-measure-water-rationed",
              "south-measure-water-reduced",
              "south-measure-water-emergency"
            ]
          },
          "close": true,
          "tone": "commit"
        },
        {
          "label": "Begin Morrow cistern rationing",
          "conditions": {
            "flag": "south-measure-plan-morrow-import"
          },
          "effects": {
            "setFlag": "south-measure-water-rationed",
            "questUpdate": {
              "quest": "names-for-the-gate",
              "stage": "decide-pump-control",
              "log": "The buried feed closes. Morrow cisterns begin a stable daily ration."
            },
            "clearFlag": [
              "south-measure-water-full",
              "south-measure-water-reduced",
              "south-measure-water-emergency"
            ]
          },
          "close": true,
          "tone": "commit"
        },
        {
          "label": "Open the isolated resident loop",
          "conditions": {
            "flag": "south-measure-plan-isolated-loop"
          },
          "effects": {
            "setFlag": "south-measure-water-reduced",
            "questUpdate": {
              "quest": "names-for-the-gate",
              "stage": "decide-pump-control",
              "log": "Noa closes the north feed and opens the relief return. South Measure keeps a reduced local flow."
            },
            "clearFlag": [
              "south-measure-water-full",
              "south-measure-water-rationed",
              "south-measure-water-emergency"
            ]
          },
          "close": true,
          "tone": "commit"
        },
        {
          "label": "Close the buried feed",
          "conditions": {
            "flag": "south-measure-plan-feed-closed"
          },
          "effects": {
            "setFlag": "south-measure-water-emergency",
            "questUpdate": {
              "quest": "names-for-the-gate",
              "stage": "decide-pump-control",
              "log": "The buried feed closes. South Measure begins emergency rationing from stored water."
            },
            "clearFlag": [
              "south-measure-water-full",
              "south-measure-water-rationed",
              "south-measure-water-reduced"
            ]
          },
          "close": true,
          "tone": "commit"
        },
        {
          "label": "Delay the water decision",
          "next": "start"
        }
      ]
    },
    "pump": {
      "lines": [
        "The operating plan is written. Susanna sets four keys beside the water slate."
